OL,3,CMan charged with murder after 'loving
OL,4,Cand devoted' man killed in 'hit-and-
OL,5,Crun'
OL,7,FA man has been charged with murder
OL,8,Fafter a 29-year-old man was killed in
OL,9,Fa suspected 'hit-and-run' in
OL,10,FWolverhampton.
OL,12,FRyan Griffiths was seriously injured
OL,13,Fwhen he was hit by a car in Burleigh
OL,14,FRoad in Merridale just before 9pm on
OL,15,FAugust 21 and died in hospital two
OL,16,Fdays later.
OL,18,FAden Wright, 26, has been charged with
OL,19,FMr Griffiths' murder and appeared at
OL,20,FWolverhampton Magistrates' Court on
OL,21,FWednesday (28 August).
